</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B9B975A754CD70880AAF2C25BDAF2D3" blockId="3.[134,2487,3373,3479]" pageId="3" pageNumber="383">
Slit-faced Bat (
<taxonomicName id="4C24ECD9754CD7088355F2C25490F2FB" authorityName="K. Andersen" authorityYear="1912" box="[1615,1774,3373,3398]" class="Mammalia" family="Nycteridae" genus="Nycteris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="383" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="aurita">Nycteris aurita</taxonomicName>
